data.name: customSqlQuery1.Sql
data.value: select (select sum(Quantity) from tbl_InvoiceDetails where InvoiceNo=i.InvoiceNo and BranchId=i.BranchId) as 'TotalQuantity', (select sum(Total) from tbl_InvoiceDetails where InvoiceNo=i.InvoiceNo and BranchId=i.BranchId) as 'SubTotal','PrintCount'=case when i.PrintCount=1 then 'ORIGINAL FOR RECIPIENT' else (case when i.PrintCount=2 then 'DUPLICATE FOR TRANSPORTER' else (case when i.PrintCount=3 then 'TRIPLICATE FOR SUPPLIER' else 'EXTRA COPY' end) end) end, i.Transporter,i.Remarks,i.TermsofDelivery,i.Address,i.DeliveryAddress,c.CINNo,c.PAN,c.GSTNo,c.CompanyName,i.InvoiceNo,convert(varchar,i.InvoiceDate,103) as 'InvoiceDate',i.ChallanNo,CONVERT(varchar,i.ChallanDate,103) as 'ChallanDate', i.OrderNo,convert(varchar,i.OrderDate,103) as 'OrderDate',i.TotalAmount,i.UserId,i.GrandTotal,(select [dbo].[ZZ_GET_AMT_IN_WORDS](i.GrandTotal)) as 'sumwords',i.Through,i.States, n.CompanyName as 'ConsigneeName',n.GSTNo as 'ConsigneeGST',n.PAN as 'ConsigneePAN',i.StateofDelivery,(i.CityofDespatch+', '+i.StateofDespatch) as 'PlaceofDespatch', (select sum(TaxValue) from dbo.tbl_InvoiceTax where InvoiceNo=i.InvoiceNo and BranchId=i.BranchId) as 'Totaltax', (select [dbo].[ZZ_GET_AMT_IN_WORDS]((select sum(TaxValue) from dbo.tbl_InvoiceTax where InvoiceNo=i.InvoiceNo and BranchId=i.BranchId))) as 'sumwordsTax' from dbo.tbl_Invoice i join dbo.tbl_CustomerMaster c on c.CustomerId=i.CustomerId join dbo.tbl_CustomerMaster n on n.CustomerId=i.Consignee where i.InvoiceNo=@InvoiceNo and BranchId=@BranchId

data.name: customSqlQuery2.Sql
data.value: select 'Items'=case when (isnull(i.Description,'')!='' and i.Description!=' ') then (m.ItemName+' ('+i.Description+')') else m.ItemName end ,(convert(varchar,i.Quantity)+' '+ m.Unit) as 'Quantity',m.ItemName,i.Description as 'ItemDescription',i.Rate,i.Total,i.HSCode from dbo.tbl_InvoiceDetails i join dbo.tbl_ItemMaster m on m.ItemId=i.ItemId where i.InvoiceNo=@InvoiceNo and i.BranchId=@BranchId
